From f10fa1919b06e0185ef8eb23bdc3e441286e509d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: v0agent <it+v0agent@vercel.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Jun 2026 10:41:53 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add Q&A moderation: JWT auth, flagged model, delete/ban/lift
 commands

- Enable real jose JWT verification using room.env.SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET (HS256)
- Add authorId to questions; enforce in-memory session bans on submit
- Flag threshold now marks questions flagged (hidden from attendees, dimmed for mods) instead of hard-hiding
- Role-aware broadcast: admins receive flagged questions, attendees do not
- New admin commands: delete_question, ban_user, lift_ban
- Send connection role in sync payload for client UI gating

Co-authored-by: v0agent <it+v0agent@vercel.com>
